related_questions.question: How can an Indian get a job in USA?
related_questions.snippet: The first is to seek a job at an MNC and hope to get posted onsite in the US. Another option is to pursue an MS degree in the US, after which you can find a job there. You cannot directly apply for jobs in the US from India (unless you have a work permit, which is expensive for companies to obtain).Feb 16, 2016
